Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.65,0:01:44.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, the maple trees on the mountain are a lot prettier too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.19,0:01:51.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the Futaba Dam sometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:52.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:56.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring along some XXX stuff then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:58.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:01:59.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother with him, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.97,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring snacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:03.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring drinks, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.14,0:02:05.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You take care of the sandwiches, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:13.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I can't make lunches on my days off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:15.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Try asking Touko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'll be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.16,0:02:22.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be happy too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.14,0:02:24.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko's sandwiches!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:25.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:32.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Later, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.11,0:02:34.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:11.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A Youkai...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.77,0:03:14.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,is eating another Youkai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.68,0:03:19.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You saw me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:20.93,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:30.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:33.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Running is futile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:36.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat you, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.30,0:03:37.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming to eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:47.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Takashi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.48,0:03:52.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You look pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:55.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.18,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! It'll burn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.95,0:04:11.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanko-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:15.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having fried squid tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:16.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How's the squid?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Cats can't eat squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.08,0:04:21.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'm not a cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.27,0:04:24.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that mark, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:30.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.13,0:04:32.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a curse on your arm, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:37.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to laugh about, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.63,0:04:53.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he lay his hands on my prey? It's positively inexcusable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And he's going to eat you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, I'd be grateful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:05:01.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but I simply can't allow him to get you before I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:03.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:10.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,let's call someone else to be your bodyguard in my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Call them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll use the Book of Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.88,0:05:16.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The Book of Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,We can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:21.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko boasted about it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.22,0:05:29.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:33.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good. Next, put that white cloth on and then stand right in the middle of the characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:35.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's to substitute a white robe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call them unless you know their name and how they look,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,so let's try to call Misuzu from before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:46.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume, place the Book of Friends and the mirror beside each other and then drop some blood on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:47.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:51.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, they'd want a fingernail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:54.75,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you can deal with Ayakashi without some compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:00.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:01.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.10,0:06:04.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,One who would protect me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.94,0:06:06.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,come forth to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:07.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:09.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:23.23,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a while, Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:27.39,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I couldn't return your name last time, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.27,0:06:29.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.19,0:06:31.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.88,0:06:34.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:35.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.10,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It spread out more than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:40.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A curse mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:45.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not familiar with curses, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.02,0:06:47.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I will send for someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.11,0:06:48.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That'd be a huge help.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:54.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Natsume-dono, you should not show any weaknesses to Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.23,0:06:58.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayakashi attack people through their weaknesses and shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Loneliness can serve as compensation for Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:08.99,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being quite rude to your master, Misuzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get too ahead of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:13.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And this coming from you, Madara?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:16.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you can call yourself his bodyguard when he has some mark now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:17.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:22.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume-dono, please forget that cat doll and call upon me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who's a cat doll?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:28.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damned rocking horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:31.53,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I shall call for Hinoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:33.45,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what? Did he say Hinoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:37.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.73,0:07:39.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:53.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Reiko! Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.22,0:07:55.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:57.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You've finally called for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:01.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My lovely Reiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:03.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those scornful eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:06.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,those thin lips... {}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with your hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.37,0:08:10.68,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did those humans bully you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:13.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those rotten humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:18.06,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I curse to death all the ones who touched you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:29.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.02,0:08:32.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a big Reiko lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:35.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.62,0:08:37.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And she hates men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:39.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:41.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Madara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:42.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:48.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that small, furry form?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.99,0:08:51.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you want Reiko to like you that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:53.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Hinoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.58,0:08:55.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume's getting scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.65,0:08:57.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,who's this fake Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her grandson, Takashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:06.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandson? What about Reiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,She died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:12.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What a short life...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.72,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I hate getting attached to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.59,0:09:25.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get closer to me, you damned man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:27.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:31.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crying for Reiko-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:43.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu-dono had said that Natsume called for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,So I got a bit excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:50.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Five Day Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:57.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Five Day Mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:02.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,This Ayakashi cannot move, and so he places marks on people passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.19,0:10:06.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,For five days, the mark will comsume their life force,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:09.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and will draw them to the owner of the mark to be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:15.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,By repeating that, the owner of the mark will gain the power to be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.38,0:10:22.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:24.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't remember which way I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.78,0:10:28.52,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably went on some path humans can not take,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and met the owner of that mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... It'll be bothersome, but I'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.04,0:10:36.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:44.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I got myself involved in some bad business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.21,0:10:48.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an Ayakashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.90,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this might be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:10.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.46,0:11:12.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It got scraped on a tree branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:14.86,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:18.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, it'll be bad if it festers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.56,0:11:20.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! There aren't any problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:21.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.90,0:11:22.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No, show m-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:33.83,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, it's really spreading.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.11,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this shadow? It's like Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.82,0:11:50.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this Merry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:55.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a horror story where some unknown creature gets closer and closer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.74,0:11:58.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You get a phone call,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:02.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and they say, "I'm Merry. I'm at the front gate now."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,After a while, another call comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:07.60,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,When you pick it up,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:11.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,they say, "I'm Merry. I'm at the front door."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have something to do with this mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:53.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.69,0:13:00.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the same face as Reiko, so don't make such a pathetic expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:01.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Hinoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.35,0:13:05.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I found out who the owner of the mark is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a powerful evil spirit that's been sealed away for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.91,0:13:11.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It uses the mark to hunt its prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.15,0:13:13.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Bit by bit, it stores its power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.22,0:13:17.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that if it eats one more, the seal will be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:19.71,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,One more? You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:20.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:26.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,And the evil spirit, unable to wait to restore its power, sends out a shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:32.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow will suck the life from you through the mark, and it'll be able to move faster and faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:38.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still slow now, and was finally able to find your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:42.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die if it touches you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.63,0:13:56.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're huge, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:00.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,My power isn't stable because of the effects of the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:03.19,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:04.30,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:05.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:08.49,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you back, Takashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:16.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange, I thought I heard his voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:20.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I eat that shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No one without the mark can touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.81,0:14:29.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter. The Five Day Mark will only last four more days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:31.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to run away for that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.87,0:14:35.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:37.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just four more days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:38.63,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.81,0:14:47.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to worry them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.72,0:14:51.43,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:55.48,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what may happen if I'm with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.17,0:15:07.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If I camp out and return by morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:09.77,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-san shouldn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.17,0:15:28.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.74,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It went into the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.82,0:15:33.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:36.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, it's a long weekend tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:41.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you fall in love with some foreigner or something, Natsume?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:43.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,How international!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:49.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:50.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Takashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.41,0:15:53.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be staying at my friend's house for the next three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.43,0:15:56.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:58.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:03.15,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no. Whose house? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:06.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, everyone's waiting! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:09.73,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.26,0:16:16.62,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.25,0:16:19.29,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cause her trouble if I'm there, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.13,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not like Reiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You like humans, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't like them when I was small.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:38.42,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,But after meeting kind people, I learned what kindness was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to run away anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.50,0:16:45.67,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become kind too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:49.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a man, so what's with the lame talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:51.41,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got that right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:58.51,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:05.66,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, it'll just be this once, but how would you like having a servant to protect you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.41,0:17:07.16,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:09.92,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A creature of light that can expel the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:13.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I will teach you how to summon one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:15.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be tough, so do you want to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:18.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,With your energy, it'll be a one-shot battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.21,0:17:21.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Either a big one will show up, or a useless little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:24.35,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hinoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:32.03,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why do you look like Reiko, yet you're a man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:48.89,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.95,0:17:52.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Rest a bit before the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.50,0:18:04.09,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll go get some fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:15.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I want... to go back home...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:43.00,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It chased after me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.82,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:58.08,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat you, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.48,0:19:01.84,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.31,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.04,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.27,0:19:10.38,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.37,0:19:18.50,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I summon thee from the paths of light,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.07,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,you who expels the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.23,0:19:29.24,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.59,0:19:37.28,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,It's tiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.49,0:19:40.33,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your servant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.24,0:20:15.25,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:17.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:19.96,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:22.14,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mark is gone as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.27,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:26.61,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:28.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:34.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Watching you, all I could see was your desire to protect important things,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:36.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,and not wanting to cause trouble for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:39.58,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,All those kinds of feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:45.21,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate people who don't treasure themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:48.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.64,0:20:57.95,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I had you tested, Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:03.01,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A test to see whether I should entrust my name to a human child or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A test?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:08.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one that made the path to lead you to the evil spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.11,0:21:10.80,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Misuzu! You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were eaten, then that would have been it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.51,0:21:16.44,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I would then take the Book of Friends for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.44,0:21:17.36,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.04,0:21:18.65,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.71,0:21:21.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:23.91,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you're interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.23,0:21:26.54,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, Natsume-dono.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.25,0:21:29.47,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall entrust my name to you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:32.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't terribly hate having my name called.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:33.81,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.61,0:21:37.88,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind being called by you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:41.64,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever find yourself in despair from humans, come to me anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.19,0:21:53.17,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Takashi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.66,0:21:56.85,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.18,0:21:59.56,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you so many times to give me the contact information!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.98,0:22:01.32,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.96,0:22:04.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:04.70,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:07.69,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how worried do you think I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.06,0:22:10.94,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind you staying at your friend's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.94,0:22:13.05,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,but you have to tell me where!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:15.46,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll I do if something happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:18.57,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I was worrying all night!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:21.20,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even get one wink of sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:21.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.99,0:22:22.87,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Back at my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:24.79,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Takashi-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.25,0:22:26.78,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes! I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.01,0:22:33.37,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Back at this kind and warm house, where I live with my precious family.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:08.34,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A long night in autumn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:09.76,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,A lively festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.17,0:24:11.55,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks coloring the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:15.12,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,The kind people I met in this city are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.33,0:24:20.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,Was I able to do something for them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:25.22,natsume,,0000,0000,0000,,
